    Type Description
    float[]

    An array of floating-point values representing the vertices and texture coordinates.
    Overrides
    Shape.GetShape()
    Remarks

    The vertices are defined in the following order:

    • Vertex positions (x, y, z)
    • Texture coordinates (u, v)
